		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Few months ago, I joined the &lt;a rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;discourse.haskell.org&#x2F;t&#x2F;haskell-security-response-team-announcement-and-q2-2023-report&#x2F;6931&quot;&gt;Haskell Security Response Team&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&#x27;ve been involved in &lt;a rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;haskell&#x2F;security-advisories&#x2F;tree&#x2F;main&#x2F;code&#x2F;hsec-tools&quot;&gt;hsec-tools&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;, which aims, in the medium terms, to support the whole security advisories infrastructure.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One of our distributions is &lt;a rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;NixOS&#x2F;nix&quot;&gt;nix&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;, so, when I had to create a docker image, I started with:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
